snippet.title: Rewrite - DYH - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to Rewrite - DYH - A game that changes every time you play!
Thank you very much for watching the video, I look forward to share this game with you. 
Get "Rewrite - DYH" for PC on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1370640/Rewrite__DYH/
